            "message": "Use shortcode <code>[link-list id=\"N\"]<\/code> in post content, where <strong>N<\/strong> is the row number below (starting from 1).\r\n\r\nExamples:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>[link-list id=\"1\"]<\/code> — displays the first block<\/li>\r\n<li><code>[link-list id=\"2\"]<\/code> — displays the second block<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\nEach block has its own <strong>Variant<\/strong> (pill or card) and <strong>Links<\/strong> list.",
